name: Jan Sahas Social Development Society
briefDescription: Jan Sahas is a social and community based organization working with socially excluded and marginalized communities particularly women and children for ensuring their overall development. The organization was formed by few youths who took up the issue of death of one child labour and two dalit labours in illegal firecrackers unit in year 2000.
